_sText:
There is 1 Battleground to play on, the player who gets to the teleport first, picks a weapon.

Included weapons are:
GS3G1, MiniGun, Deagle, Scout, Famas, AWP, M4A1 Ak47 Galil M3 P90 MP5

This map requires the "Noblock-Plugin" to work properly!
There are 60 player slots so it can easily go on any server.
There are 4 different songs, beginning to play when a player reaches the teleport.

Special Thanks:
AleXXT | Dr.mINI

This map will no longer be supported.
